      • runTestProgramFromFile

        public static void runTestProgramFromFile(java.lang.String file)
        Runs a test of all implementations on the file specified. Since the data is read in as a string, it only tests on strings. To test on data other then strings, run runTestProgram()
        Parameters:
        file - File to run tests on.

      • printQueue

        public static <E> void printQueue(IQueue<E> queue)
        Dequeues all elements in the passed queue and prints them to the console. If there are 1000 or more elements, it skips printing out all the elements.
        Parameters:
        queue - The queue to print.

      • printStack

        public static <E> void printStack(IStack<E> stack)
        Pops all elements out of the passed stack and prints them to the console. If there are 1000 or more elements in the stack it skips printing them to the console.
        Parameters:
        stack - The stack to print.
